gstore

Class GStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • gstore.GStore

  • public class GStore
extends Object
    Common API to store and retrieve objects to/from a searchable store, with a time pointer function. GStore is not thread safe for the same store: only one instance of GStore is intended per path.

        public String addn(ogdl.IGraph g)
            throws Exception
        addn allows several objects to be inserted/updated at once. The input graph describes the objects. Those with ID will be updated, those without are new. Format: _ id $id_1 fields Unknown IDs are represented by $id_N TODO: make this a transaction
